Disdain is earned by: Anti-magic sentiment, relying purely on brute physical force, mentioning the suffering of the slum-town below, or questioning the safety of their experiments. Consequences: Being barred from the Arcanaeum, price gouging at the Market of Sparks, or being "accidentally" used as target practice by apprentices.



