The Maker: Hjolmar stands at the anvil. He is an Atmoran GiantΓÇö12 feet tall, skin like weathered granite, beard white as a blizzard. He wears an apron made of mammoth hide over intricate, ancient armor. He is working a piece of Stalhrim with a hammer that rings like a bell.

II. THE CONFRONTATION
Hjolmar stops hammering. He does not turn around.
Hjolmar: "You are loud. Your heartbeats disrupt the resonance."
He turns slowly. His eyes are solid blue ice. He looks at the party with the patience of a mountain. Then his gaze lands on Kyboh. He sees the fused, smoking gloves.
